        "jsCode": "const response = $input.first().json;\nconst text = response.candidates[0].content.parts[0].text;\nconst clean = text.replace(/```json|```/g, '').trim();\nconst parsed = JSON.parse(clean);\n\n// ✅ 改用 .first() 取代 .item，避免 Multiple matches 錯誤\nconst original = $('Code in JavaScript3').first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    ...parsed,\n    resumeLink: original.resumeLink,\n    phone: original.phone,\n    emailAddress: original.emailAddress,\n    contactLink: original.contactLink\n  }\n}];\n"
